  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Engro Pakistan Emergency Investment Facility</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The emergency loan is expected to help the Company deal with declining fertilizer sales and delays in completion of its new fertilizer plant that are due to the large scale floods in Pakistan.  The facilitys objective is to smooth the operation and output and support the Company to respond quickly to the recovery in fertilizer demand once agricultural production picks up again.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed IFC investment in Engro Fertilizers Limited (Engro or the Company), consists of a subordinated loan of up to $30 million to help mitigate the impact from the recent floods on their fertilizer business.</narrative>
  </description>
